#. type: document
#: around-desktop/around-desktop.tex :10
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "At first glance, you will notice many similarities between Ubuntu and "
#| "other operating systems such as Windows or Mac \\acronym{OS~X}. This is "
#| "because they are all based on the concept of a graphical user interface "
#| "(\\gls{GUI})\\dash that is, you use your mouse to navigate the desktop, "
#| "open programs, move files, and perform most other tasks. In short, things "
#| "are very visually oriented, which means it is important for you to become "
